SIMPLE: put_paid_to
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: put paid to
<hw>put paid to</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
put an end to.</def> <specif>Hence:</specif> <def>To prove false; to
discredit; <as>as, Galileo's observations <ex>put paid to</ex> the
notion that the Earth was the center of the universe</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To defeat; to cause the defeat of.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><q>The Argentine's infamous Hand of God goals when he punched the
ball into the net, and a spectacular solo effort <qex>put paid to</qex>
England in the last eight . . .</q> <rj><qau>Sunday Times, 17 May
1998</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Putredinous</ent>⟦br⟧
